Colombia Brokerage Interbolsa Advances on Stock Repurchase

-- B y   B l a k e   S c h m i d t
-- 
2011-05-27T20:20:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-27/colombia-brokerage-interbolsa-advances-on-stock-repurchase-plan.html
Interbolsa SA,  Colombia ’s largest
securities brokerage, held at 2,700 pesos following an earlier
gain that was the most in four months after the company said it
plans to repurchase as much as 20.3 billion pesos ($11 million)
of stock.  Interbolsa was unchanged at 4 p.m. New York time, after
earlier rising as much as 3.5 percent, the most since Jan. 25.
The company disclosed the stock repurchase plan on the website
of the nation’s securities regulator after the close of trading
yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blake  Schmidt in Bogota at 
